# Linear Centroids Hypothesis — official paper code (git submodule)

This directory is populated by the upstream repository. It is **not**
shipped inside Linear Centroid Experiments; add it locally with:

```bash
git submodule add https://github.com/ThomasWalker1/LinearCentroidsHypothesis.git third_party/LinearCentroidsHypothesis
git submodule update --init --recursive
```

If you cloned this repo without submodules:

```bash
git submodule update --init --recursive
```

Expected file after init: `centroids.py` (see paper repo).

Our code accesses it only through `lce.centroid_adapter`.
